/* Onboarding */
"Save the prompts you actually use" = "本当に使うプロンプトを保存";
"ChatGPT · Claude · Midjourney · ComfyUI · Coze. One vault for all of them." = "ChatGPT・Claude・Midjourney・ComfyUI・Coze。すべて 1 つの保管庫で。";
"Fill in the blanks" = "空欄を埋めるだけ";
"Use {{variables}} to template your prompts. Tap a row, fill the blanks, copy." = "{{変数}}でテンプレ化。行をタップして空欄を埋めれば、コピーできます。";
